summary:
• Knowledge of Process Engineering, CO2 capture, catalysis and water treatment.
• Data analysis of waster treatment plant.
• Design of activated sludge system.
• 5 papers on modelling, using MATLAB software, published in high ranking journals.
• Experienced in leading R&D projects.
• Experienced in synthesizing and characterizing of the porous materials.
• Worked with GC, TGA, SEM, XRD, N2 Physisorption, and FTIR and analyzed the 
results.
• Familiar with almost all laboratory equipment.
• Familiar with OHSAS and ISO.
